{"type":"article","id":2900,"title":"六四屠城图片全览 前言","uid":16,"topics":[149,998],"contents":"鉴于大多数机场屏蔽了bannedbook.org，我就把这个64历史图片的帖子直接搬过来吧。<br>\n<br>\n当然，你也可以通过archive.today查看快照，或者通过类似<a href=\"https://via.hypothes.is/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://via.hypothes.is/</a>的网站间接查看。<br>\n<br>\n来自<a href=\"https://www.bannedbook.org/books/64photo/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bannedbook.org/books/64photo/</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/lQ8kTH0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lQ8kTH0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/lQ8kTH0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n六四屠城图片全览 第一编：和平请愿<br>\n何处招魂－－民主之光耀邦－－中央美院敬挽<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/W6yuxOJ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W6yuxOJ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/W6yuxOJ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n心焦力瘁顾大局撒手先去！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1k6uy0G.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1k6uy0G.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1k6uy0G.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n倒下了﹐一面民族的旗帜倒下了！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JK678nx.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JK678nx.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JK678nx.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n小学生也上街游行<mark>支</mark>持大哥哥大姐姐的正义行动。他们打出「打倒官倒」的牌子<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XYaCstV.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XYaCstV.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/XYaCstV.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n愚民政策该收场了！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gkGUAl4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gkGUAl4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gkGUAl4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n绝食请愿．．．．．．<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/YkgzcAt.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YkgzcAt.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/YkgzcAt.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n工会声援团--<mark>支</mark>持绝食学生 “工会来了﹗”<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JH2vFj5.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JH2vFj5.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JH2vFj5.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n僧人重返「红尘」<mark>支</mark>持绝食学生<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/hoTyKHB.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hoTyKHB.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/hoTyKHB.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n从最传统到最现代的中国人都在广场上找到了共同的目标。一位和尚在天安门广场发表演讲<mark>支</mark>持学生<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9yjhVpE.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9yjhVpE.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9yjhVpE.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n万里说学生运动是爱国行动 ！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/6Z6W5FP.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6Z6W5FP.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/6Z6W5FP.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n《新华社》1989年5月16日<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bv7UeyI.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bv7UeyI.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bv7UeyI.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n《北京青年报》17日夜在天安门广场进行民意测验——多数认为学运是爱国运动,请大家仔细看，后面只有7个人认为中共会镇压！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/zNqaxzT.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zNqaxzT.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zNqaxzT.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n百万人潮！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/New6Nis.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/New6Nis.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/New6Nis.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n上海外滩，复旦、上海社会科学院队伍，举有“法盲，江泽民，辞职”等指责江泽民不当处理导报的标语<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/a0iHROT.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/a0iHROT.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/a0iHROT.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n高举的标语上写着：“请问邓小平，我的孩子在绝食、挨饿，你的孩子在干什么！”<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kYDbVTQ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kYDbVTQ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kYDbVTQ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n“铲除官倒”！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NJplcdx.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NJplcdx.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NJplcdx.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n赵紫阳同志代表中央政治局常委发表书面谈话，充分肯定学生的爱国热情,党和政府绝不会“秋后算账”。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qp6tjbx.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qp6tjbx.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qp6tjbx.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n《经济日报》1989年5月19日第2219号 头版。劝食书<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/D2KGftR.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D2KGftR.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/D2KGftR.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n北京大学国际经济系在广场的绝食学生打出横幅﹕「我有一个梦」。一百万群众继续游行声援学生；各界知名人士紧急呼吁对话<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/CjZlMBh.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CjZlMBh.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/CjZlMBh.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n不管大瓶小瓶能装水就有水平不能装水就退瓶<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xZEQ27m.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xZEQ27m.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xZEQ27m.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n小平您好－－糊涂<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/DULVYFT.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DULVYFT.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/DULVYFT.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-07-31","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}